Timeline (Suggested Weekend Project)
Phase	Tasks	Duration
Day 1 Morning	Unbox, inventory parts, review wiring diagram	1-2 hrs
Day 1 Afternoon	Disassemble RC car, mount ESP32 + motor driver	2-3 hrs
Day 1 Evening	Wire motors, test basic forward/backward	1-2 hrs
