Total: ~12-15 hours over a weekend

Risks & Mitigations
Risk	Mitigation
Motors draw too much current	Use separate battery for motors, or ensure 2A+ supply
Radar false positives	Tune sensitivity, add delay before reacting
Car too fast for reaction time	Limit PWM speed to 50-60%
Wiring mistakes	Double-check with multimeter before powering on
