‚úì RadarRover Ready!
Tuning Tips üîß
Problem	Solution
Car too fast	Lower
BASE_SPEED
to 100-120
Hits walls	Increase
SAFE_DISTANCE
to 50-60
Turns too much	Reduce
TURN_DURATION
to 300
Jerky movement	Increase
SENSOR_DELAY
to 100
Motors spin wrong way	Swap
IN1/IN2
or
IN3/IN4
values
